---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Boat Upholstery" description="Marine upholstery specialists in Brisbane's Bayside. Yacht cushions, boat seats, marine vinyl. Quality materials for harsh marine conditions.">
  <div class="px-4 py-8">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Boats</h1>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <div class="md:col-span-2">
        <p class="text-stone-700 mb-4">
          Living in Brisbane's Bayside, we understand the demands of the marine environment. Our boat upholstery is designed to withstand sun, salt, and moisture while looking great season after season.
        </p>
        <p class="text-stone-700 mb-4">
          We use quality marine-grade vinyl and fabrics that are UV resistant, easy to clean, and built to handle the harsh conditions of life on the water.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Our Marine Services</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-stone-700 mb-6 space-y-1">
          <li>Yacht cushions</li>
          <li>Marine vinyl seating</li>
          <li>Boat interior trim</li>
          <li>Top-sewn seams for durability</li>
          <li>UV resistant materials</li>
          <li>Custom boat covers</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Quality Materials</h2>
        <p class="text-stone-700 mb-6">
          We source only the best marine-grade materials that resist mould, mildew, and fading. Our workmanship ensures your boat upholstery will look great and perform well for years to come.
        </p>

        <img src="/images/IMG_0916-Medium.jpg" alt="Yacht cockpit cushions" class="w-full rounded shadow" />
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="bg-stone-100 p-4 rounded">
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-2">Why Choose Us?</h3>
          <ul class="text-stone-700 text-sm space-y-2">
            <li>✓ Local Bayside business</li>
            <li>✓ 40+ years experience</li>
            <li>✓ Marine-grade materials</li>
            <li>✓ Custom work to spec</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-amber-50 p-4 rounded border border-amber-200">
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-2">Get a Quote</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-700 text-sm mb-3">
            Send us photos of your boat interior for a free, no-obligation quote.
          </p>
          <a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-amber-600 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded hover:bg-amber-700 transition text-sm">
            Contact Us
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
